<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM1.3">
<l>mattanaṉ ṉaṟumalar murukkamalar koṇṭumup pōtumuṉ ṉaṭivaṇaṅkit</l>
<l>tattuva miliyeṉṟu neñcerintu vācakat taḻittuṉṉai vaitiṭāmē</l>
<l>kottalar pūṅkaṇai toṭuttukkoṇṭu kōvinta ṉeṉpatōr pērēḻuti</l>
<l>vittakaṉ vēṅkaṭa vāṇaṉeṉṉum viḷakkiṉiṟ pukaveṉṉai vitikkiṟṟiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>So that we do not scold you burning with anger—saying ‘[He is] untruthful!’—</l>
<l>[and] despising [You] through words,</l>
<l>Will you be able to fix an arrow of flowers that blossom in clusters, write [on it]</l>
<l rend="indent">the unique name Govinda,</l>
<l>and direct me in such a way that [I] enter</l>
<l rend="indent">the Light that is the Dweller of Veṅkaṭam, the Mysterious [Lord]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
